A video of a couple using reportedly using a child to steal items at a creche has
surfaced on social media. The couple allegedly uses the child to steal at crèches while
they pretend to go through the crèches they go into. In the video, the couple can be seen going through the crèche,
as soon as they go into another room the child remains behind and takes
something that is on a table and then hides it between the pants and t-shirt. The couple reportedly came to the crèche last week Friday,
pretending to be interested in enrolling their child at the crèche. The couple has allegedly done the same thing in the Helderkruin
area, west of Johannesburg. According to News24, the Roodepoort police spokesperson
Captain Juanita Yorke said although no case had been opened yet, police were
still investigating the incident. 